Project Overview: NFT Collection Collaboration Tool
Purpose: A platform connecting up-and-coming NFT collections with artists, developers, marketers, and promoters.
Functionality:
- Users can create profiles.
- Users can list their skills and specify what they are looking for.
- Project showcase feature for displaying past work.
- Rating system for collaborations to build trust.
Technical Stack
Framework: Next.js 15 (using src/app structure for routing)
Authentication: Firebase for X/Twitter authentication
Database: Firebase for user data and real-time updates
UI Libraries
@chakra-ui/react: For accessible and customizable UI components.
@emotion/react and @emotion/styled: For styling components with CSS-in-JS.
framer-motion: For animations and transitions in React.